    "reduce civilian harm and protect soldiers from undue levels of suffering leading to moral injury.",
    "However, processes must be instituted to measure changes to decision-making in human-AI teams.",
    "This is particularly acute with the systemic replacement of cognitive functions by AI that humans would normally be tasked with in targeting decisions to be morally and legally responsible for those decisions.",
    "The thesis of this chapter is that good apples can become 'cooked' if they are poorly paired with AI systems including detaching from responsibility for decisions, becoming moral crumple zones, suffering moral injury, or becoming extreme moral witnesses.",
